-4 group-hover:text-brand-600 transition-colors line-clamp-3 leading-tight\">How to Prevent Bed Bugs While Traveling</h2><p class=\"text-surface-600 line-clamp-3 mb-6 flex-grow leading-relaxed\">Traveling is fun, but bringing bed bugs home is not. Learn how to inspect hotel rooms and protect your luggage.</p><span class=\"inline-flex items-center text-accent-500 font-black tracking-wide uppercase text-sm group-hover:text-accent-600 transition-colors mt-auto\">Read More<span class=\"ml-2 transform group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform\">→</span></span></div></a></article><article class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300 border border-surface-100 group flex flex-col \"><a class=\"block flex-grow flex flex-col\" href=\"/blog/identifying-common-household-ants\"><div class=\"relative overflow-hidden aspect-video\"><img src=\"/images/blog-3.jpg\" alt=\"Identifying Common Household Ants\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-700\" loading=\"lazy\"/><span class=\"absolute top-4 left-4 bg-accent-500 text-brand-900 text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-wider px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full shadow-md\">Pest Control</span></div><div class=\"p-6 lg:p-8 flex flex-col justify-center flex-grow \"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 text-sm text-surface-500 font-medium mb-4\"><span class=\"flex items-center\"><span class=\"mr-2 text-accent-500\">📅</span><time dateTime=\"2026-06-28\">2026-06-28</time></span><span class=\"flex items-center\"><span class=\"mr-2 text-accent-500\">⏱️</span>5 min read</span></div><h2 class=\"text-xl lg:text-2xl font-black text-brand-900 mb-4 group-hover:text-brand-600 transition-colors line-clamp-3 leading-tight\">Identifying Common Household Ants</h2><p class=\"text-surface-600 line-clamp-3 mb-6 flex-grow leading-relaxed\">Not all ants are the same. Learn to identify the different types of ants that might invade your kitchen.</p><span class=\"i